General.Name: Sjóvá-Almennar tryggingar hf
General.Description: Sjóvá-Almennar tryggingar hf. operates as an insurance company in Iceland. The company offers motor vehicle, family and home, life and critical illness, medical cost, life and health, and travel insurance products for individuals. It also provides commercial insurance products, such as fire and commercial property insurance; public and product liability, employer's liability, directors and officers liability, professional indemnity, and commercial liability insurance; operation interruption insurance; vessel crew, hull and machinery, and catch and fishing gear/tackle insurance; vessel cargo, transport cargo, and purse seine insurance; baggage, sickness and accidents on travelling, and cancelation insurance; and insurance products for employees and leaders, including life and critical illness, accident insurance, and medical cost insurance products. The company is based in Reykjavík, Iceland. Sjóvá-Almennar tryggingar hf. was founded in 1918 and is based in Reykjavík, Iceland.
